Class ListObserverRegistry<TypeToReturn,SOAPFaultType>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.alexgilleran.icesoap.observer.registry.ObserverRegistry<List<TypeToReturn>,SOAPFaultType>
      • com.alexgilleran.icesoap.observer.registry.ListObserverRegistry<TypeToReturn,SOAPFaultType>
  • Type Parameters:
    TypeToReturn - The type that will be returned by the observers.
    SOAPFaultType - The type of the SOAP Fault envelope that will be returned in the event of an HTTP 500 error.

    public class ListObserverRegistry<TypeToReturn,SOAPFaultType>
extends ObserverRegistry<List<TypeToReturn>,SOAPFaultType>
    Extension of ObserverRegistry to deal with ListRequests. Contains extra methods to deal specifically with individual items in a list.
    Author:
    Alex Gilleran
